![logo](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/heinzelmannchen/heinzelmannchen/master/Heinzelmannchen.png)
Start managing your own templates, to be increase your efficiency.

```
$ npm install heinzelmannchen-cli -g
$ cd yourProject
$ heinzel init
```
MORE CONTENT


### Authors and Contributors
